CREATED:20241227T232005Z
DESCRIPTION:Appointment Time: Starts at 12:00 PM\nYou must physically be in
  Massachusetts at the time of your visit\, due to state requirements.  You 
 will be seen via MyHealth Video and can use the MyChart app on a smartphone
  or tablet\, or MyHealth on a computer to connect.   \nBefore Your Visit:\n
 Please complete the Pre-Visit Update up to three days before your visit. If
  your estimated co-payment is displayed\, please pay it prior to the visit.
  Click here for more information on copays. \nYou may receive a telephone c
 all from our staff 10-20 minutes before your appointment time to gather inf
 ormation including your medications\, allergies\, vitals\, and reason(s) fo
 r the visit.\nReview the Behavioral Health policies and notices prior to yo
 ur video visit appointment.  *Notice: no action is needed on these document
 s at this time.\nJoin your video visit from a private location\, such as yo
 ur home\, a private office\, or the home of a family member. Select a locat
 ion that will ensure both audio and video privacy for your visit. Do not jo
 in a video visit while driving—your visit provider will cancel the appointm
 ent and ask that you reschedule for a time when it is safe to conduct the v
 isit.\nYou may invite others to your video visit by clicking the "View and 
 Invite Participants" button and entering their email address.  This will se
 nd them a direct link to join the visit.\nAt the Time of Your Visit:\nLog i
 nto MyChart if using a mobile device or MyHealth on a computer 10 minutes b
 efore your appointment time.\nSelect the video visit appointment.\nSelect t
 he green BEGIN VISIT button. (Button is enabled 10 minutes prior to your ap
 pointment time.)\nSelect the green JOIN CALL button when it becomes enabled
 .\nPlease wait for your provider to connect\, as they may be wrapping up a 
 visit with another patient and will be with you shortly.\n\nIf you have que
 stions about the video visit\, please contact your provider's office.  If y
 ou need technical assistance\, review our Video Visit Help Center or contac
 t us at 617-559-8057\, Monday-Friday\, 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T123449Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Initial Specialty Video (Video Visit) with Nathalie Alexis\, PSYD
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
