DESCRIPTION:Andona’s 68th Annual Clown Town fundraiser is back for 2024 wit
 h many exciting firsts!  As always\, you will find plenty of fun for childr
 en and adults of all ages with Carnival Rides\, Games\, Food\, Live Music\,
  Face Painting\, Sand Art and much more!\n\nNew this year\, Andover’s belov
 ed spring carnival is hosting an extra day.  The carnival will run Friday\,
  Saturday & SUNDAY.\n\nAlso new this year\, Oak and Iron Brewing Co. will p
 rovide a Beer Garden at the park on Saturday\, May 18th from 12-7pm. \n\nA 
 third NEW Fiesta Shows to provide carnival rides\, games\, and food.  Fiest
 a provides rides and games to well-known New England attractions including 
 the Topsfield and Marshfield Fairs.  \n\nLive performances to include the A
 ndover High School Jazz Band and several The Real School of Music bands.\n\
 nCarnival Lineup \n\nFriday\, May 17th 6-10 pm - Carnival Rides\, Games & F
 ood\n\nSaturday\, May 18th 10 am-8 pm* - Carnival Rides\, Games & Food\n 10
 -4 Face Painting\, Sand Art\, Kiddie Games\n 12-7 Oak & Iron Beer Garden\n 
 4-8 Live performances by The Real School of Music\n\nSunday\, May 19th 10-4
  pm - Carnival Rides\, Games\, & Food\nSensory Friendly Hour 10AM-11AM\n\nw
 ww.fiestashows.com for ticket details\n\nAndona is a registered non-profit.
   All proceeds from Clown Town go to Andover schools\, youth programs\, sch
 olarships\, and summer camp for children of Andover families in need.\n\nww
 w.andona.org for more info\nThank you to our Sponsors & Supports\n\nGrand S
 tand - Pfizer\n\nBig Top\nT&B Landscaping and Irrigation\nApex Roofing\nPaj
 azetovic & Company\n \nNorth Andover Orthodontics\nSerene Moments LLC\nCrea
 tive Learning for Children DBA Kaleidoscope\nNEWPRO Home Solutions\nAndover
  Landscape Design & Construction\, LLC\nAndover Pediatric Dentistry / Dr. M
 aritza Morell\nAndover Soccer Association\nPrimrose\nCapital Construction C
 ompany\nLaunch Methuen\nBlackdog Builders\, Inc.\nMaster Shin's Martial Art
  school\nTown Dog\nTaste Buds Kitchen\nAndover Animal Hospital\nAndover Sum
 mer at Phillips Academy\nAndover Orthodontics\nRoyal Jewelers \nFred Church
 \nEnterprise Bank\nBellmore's Transportation\nDalton & Finegold LLP\nBlackd
 og Builders\, Inc.\n34 Park\nUltimate Perk\nChrist Church Andover\nDylan & 
 Petes Ice Cream\nStop & Shop\nOak & Iron Brewery \nFlagship Press\nMorris\,
  Rossi & Hayes Law Firm\nReal School of Music\nAndover Center for History &
  Culture\nWacky Candy Shack
LAST-MODIFIED:20240517T190033Z
LOCATION:Corner of Chestnut St & Bartlet St Andover MA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Clown Town 2024
