DESCRIPTION:(617) 265-1217\n224 Boston Street is a neighborhood restaurant 
 in Dorchester. Serving contemporary all-American comfort food during the di
 nner hour\, it lets diners get anything from a great cheeseburger or salad 
 to delicious mac 'n cheese and dessert. The most popular dishes at 224 incl
 ude the homestyle meatloaf\, tacos on homemade tortillas\, and Short Rib Ma
 c & Cheese.\n\nAt 224 Boston Street\, guests can eat inside or outside at t
 he beautiful patio setting. Diners on the go can also grab some takeout and
  enjoy it elsewhere. For people that have a busy night planned or don’t lik
 e waiting\, 224 offers the option to make reservations.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230201T082906Z
LOCATION:224 Boston St  Dorchester\, MA United States 02125
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:224 Boston Street Tavern & Restaurant
TRANSP:OPAQUE
