DESCRIPTION:Appointment Time: Starts at 9:20 AM\nYou must physically be in 
 Massachusetts at the time of your visit\, due to state requirements.  You w
 ill be seen via MyHealth Video and can use the MyChart app on a smartphone 
 or tablet\, or MyHealth on a computer to connect.   \nBefore Your Visit:\nR
 eview our Video Visit Help Center to get the most out of your video visit.\
 nPlease complete the Pre-Visit Update up to three days before your visit. I
 f your estimated co-payment is displayed\, please pay it prior to the visit
 . Click here for more information on copays. \nYou may receive a telephone 
 call from our staff 10-20 minutes before your appointment time to gather in
 formation including your medications\, allergies\, vitals\, and reason(s) f
 or the visit.\nJoin your video visit from a private location\, such as your
  home\, a private office\, or the home of a family member. Select a locatio
 n that will ensure both audio and video privacy for your visit. Do not join
  a video visit while driving—your visit provider will cancel the appointmen
 t and ask that you reschedule for a time when it is safe to conduct the vis
 it.\nYou may invite others to your video visit by clicking the "View and In
 vite Participants" button and entering their email address.  This will send
  them a direct link to join the visit.\nAt the Time of Your Visit:\nLog int
 o MyChart if using a mobile device or MyHealth on a computer 10 minutes bef
 ore your appointment time.\nSelect the video visit appointment.\nSelect the
  green BEGIN VISIT button. (Button is enabled 10 minutes prior to your appo
 intment time.)\nSelect the green JOIN CALL button when it becomes enabled.\
 nPlease wait for your provider to connect\, as they may be wrapping up a vi
 sit with another patient and will be with you shortly.\n\nIf you have quest
 ions about the video visit\, please contact your provider's office.  If you
  need technical assistance\, review our Video Visit Help Center or contact 
 us at 617-559-8057\, Monday-Friday\, 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T123449Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Video Visit (Video Visit) with Amee Rathod\, MD
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
