 tals\, and reason(s) for the visit.   This telephone call may come from a n
 umber you do not recognize.\n\nAt the Time of Your Visit:\nYour provider wi
 ll contact you by phone.  If your provider is delayed in calling you\, they
  may be wrapping up a visit with another patient and will call you shortly.
