DESCRIPTION:Appointment Time: Starts at 11:30 AM\nYou must physically be in
  Massachusetts at the time of your visit\, due to state requirements.  You 
 will be seen via MyHealth Video and can use the MyChart app on a smartphone
  or tablet\, or MyHealth on a computer to connect.   \nBefore Your Visit:\n
 Review our Video Visit Help Center to get the most out of your video visit.
 \n*NEW*: Please complete the Pre-Visit Update up to three days before your 
 visit. If your estimated co-payment is displayed\, please pay it prior to t
 he visit. Click here for more information on copays. \nYou may receive a te
 lephone call from our staff 10-20 minutes before your appointment time to g
 ather information including your medications\, allergies\, vitals\, and rea
 son(s) for the visit.\nAt the Time of Your Visit:\nLog into MyChart if usin
 g a mobile device or MyHealth on a computer 10 minutes before your appointm
 ent time.\nSelect the video visit appointment.\nSelect the green BEGIN VISI
 T button. (Button is enabled 10 minutes prior to your appointment time.)\nS
 elect the green JOIN CALL button when it becomes enabled.\nPlease wait for 
 your provider to connect\, as they may be wrapping up a visit with another 
 patient and will be with you shortly.\n\nIf you have questions about the vi
 deo visit\, please contact your provider's office.  If you need technical a
 ssistance\, review our Video Visit Help Center or contact us at 617-559-805
 7\, Monday-Friday\, 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T123449Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:OB Video Visit with Helen M. Dajer\, CNM
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
