DESCRIPTION:Appointment Time: Starts at 1:30 PM\nPhone: 617-657-6444\n\nYou
  must physically be in Massachusetts at the time of your telephone visit\, 
 due to state requirements. \n\nBefore Your Visit:\nPlease verify or update 
 your contact information under Personal Information.   \n\nComplete the Pre
 -Visit Update up to three days before your visit.\n\nPlease view this video
  and note any questions you may have - Welcome to Pregnancy Video\n\nYou ma
 y receive a telephone call from an OBGYN staff member a few days prior to y
 our visit\, to ensure you are comfortable completing the Pre-Visit Update a
 nd to schedule subsequent visits your your OB provider.     \n\n\nAt the Ti
 me of Your Visit:\nAn OBGYN nurse will contact you by phone.  If the nurse 
 is delayed in calling you\, they may be wrapping up a visit with another pa
 tient and will call you shortly. This call will take approximately 30 minut
 es.\nPlease note that it is important to both complete the questionnaires a
 nd view the linked video prior to your phone call\, so that we may answer a
 ny questions you may have!\nIf you do not receive a phone call within 15 mi
 nutes of your scheduled appointment time\, please contact the department of
 fice number\, above\, for assistance.\nThank you! We look forward to provid
 ing you with excellent care.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T123449Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Virtual - Welcome to Pregnancy with
TRANSP:OPAQUE
