DESCRIPTION:Appointment Time: Starts at 11:00 AM\nYou must physically be in
  Massachusetts at the time of your visit\, due to state requirements.  You 
 will be seen via MyHealth Video and can use the MyChart app on a smartphone
  or tablet\, or MyHealth on a computer to connect.   \nBefore Your Visit:\n
 Review our Video Visit Help Center to get the most out of your video visit.
 \nPlease complete the Pre-Visit Update up to three days before your visit. 
 If your estimated co-payment is displayed\, please pay it prior to the visi
 t. Click here for more information on copays. \nYou may receive a telephone
  call from our staff 10-20 minutes before your appointment time to gather i
 nformation including your medications\, allergies\, vitals\, and reason(s) 
 for the visit.\nJoin your video visit from a private location\, such as you
 r home\, a private office\, or the home of a family member. Select a locati
 on that will ensure both audio and video privacy for your visit. Do not joi
 n a video visit while driving—your visit provider will cancel the appointme
 nt and ask that you reschedule for a time when it is safe to conduct the vi
 sit.\nYou may invite others to your video visit by clicking the "View and I
 nvite Participants" button and entering their email address.  This will sen
 d them a direct link to join the visit.\nAt the Time of Your Visit:\nLog in
 to MyChart if using a mobile device or MyHealth on a computer 10 minutes be
 fore your appointment time.\nSelect the video visit appointment.\nSelect th
 e green BEGIN VISIT button. (Button is enabled 10 minutes prior to your app
 ointment time.)\nSelect the green JOIN CALL button when it becomes enabled.
 \nPlease wait for your provider to connect\, as they may be wrapping up a v
 isit with another patient and will be with you shortly.\n\nIf you have ques
 tions about the video visit\, please contact your provider's office.  If yo
 u need technical assistance\, review our Video Visit Help Center or contact
  us at 617-559-8057\, Monday-Friday\, 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250911T033441Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Video Visit (Video Visit) with Anna J. Groskin\, MD
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
