DESCRIPTION:(603) 356-7100 ext. 406\nLedges panoramic restaurant offers sup
 erior service\, a friendly atmosphere and award-winning cuisine. Diners enj
 oy breathtaking mountain views\, candlelit dining and beautiful decor.  Off
 ering both indoor seating and limited outdoor deck dining (summer only and 
 first come\, first served).  The panoramic mountain views are second to non
 e and a highlight to the Ledges dining experience.  Featuring locally grown
  produce and the freshest ingredients available\, Ledges offers creative ni
 ghtly specials to compliment the full menu of contemporary New England cuis
 ine.  Executive Chef\, Kevin Bush leads the team of culinary expertise in c
 reating imaginative dishes with a traditional New England flair.  The fresh
 est New England seafood and the best cuts of prime meats are the signature 
 of Ledges Restaurant.    The dinner menu offers many gluten-free items and 
 a daily vegetarian/vegan entree is offered nightly.   Wine Spectator "Award
  of Excellence" recipient since 1995.
